    static private let plainTalk = NSMutableAttributedString(string: "Plain Talk: How Poolu works\n\n• Poolu does not buy, sell, or take possession of     any lottery tickets, or share in any lottery     winnings*\r• Poolu pools only count for jackpot winning     tickets\r• Winning ticket holders receive much more in     winnings of the jackpot (typically 50%). The     poolers split the rest (pro-rated on a per entry     basis)**\r• Poolu does not accept multi-draw tickets (yet)\r\rHOW TO POOLU\r• Tickets are purchased BY YOU using the existing     distribution channels (Wawa, 711, Sheetz, etc…)\r• YOU then scan them into your account via the     Poolu app\'s OCR camera function.\r• The Poolu app verifies the authenticity of the     ticket by…(takes about 5 minutes)\r\t1. Verifying the ticket is a real Powerball/Mega  \t    Millions lottery ticket  \t2. For the upcoming drawing\r\t3. Cross-checks it against all other tickets in  \t    the pool to make sure it isn’t a duplicate of  \t    someone else’s ticket already in an open  \t    pool. \r• Immediately after a lottery drawing Poolu will     cross check all tickets in the pool against the     drawn numbers and publish the results in \"Pool     Results\". If a ticket in a pool matches all the     numbers in the Powerball/Mega Millions drawing     and wins the jackpot, we will immediately notify     the appropriate state lottery officials that a Poolu     pool holds the winning ticket, as well as notifying     all members of the pool.\r\to \"Pool Results\"\r• Winning Numbers\n\tThe winning numbers for that particular  \tdrawing.\r• Jackpot Value\n\tThe Value of the Jackpot at drawing time.\r• Pool Win the Jackpot?\n\tDoes your pool have a jackpot winning ticket?\r• Jackpot Share\n \tIf the jackpot winning ticket is yours, how  \tmuch is it worth?\r• Pooler\'s share\n\tThe \"Pooler\'s Share\" you are entitled to.\r• My Winnings\n\tDid you personally win any non-jackpot  \tmoney.\r• We will immediately turn over to the lottery(s) all     appropriate identifying information on all pool     members and their winning share amount to \n   guarantee the integrity of the pool. This     guarantees that anyone holding the jackpot     winning ticket in a Poolu pool cannot cash-in the     winnings for themselves.\r• We will also cross check all tickets to see if they     are worth any winnings—You have a 1-24 chance     of winning something in Powerball or Mega     Millions—so if you won $50—we’ll let you know!!\r• NEVER EVER THROW ANY TICKETS AWAY.     YOU STILL NEED THEM TO CASH IN IF YOU     WIN!\r\r*In the case that a Poolu pool hits the jackpot, Poolu retains the right to charge the pool for any legal, accounting and administrative costs associated with distributing the winnings to the pool members by Poolu or any state lottery or state agency. Poolu does not profit off of the winnings of the pool.  \r\r**The payout values shown in the \"Pools\" and \"Pool Results\" tab are estimates. Final payout amounts for jackpot winning pools will be calculated after the winning drawing. \"Pools\" and \"Pool Results\" is for informational purposes only. Final disbursement allocations will be calculated by our accounting firm. It is possible to have more than one winner of a jackpot. This happens when two people play the same numbers. In this scenario the pools will be prorated.\r\r", attributes: [
        .font: UIFont(name: "Avenir-Roman", size: 14.0)!,
        .foregroundColor: UIColor(red: 147.0 / 255.0, green: 149.0 / 255.0, blue: 152.0 / 255.0, alpha: 1.0),
        .kern: 0.0
        ])
    
    
    
